# WP Stat (available in Chrome Web Store)

A Google Chrome Extention showing in toolbar daily hits on owned Wordpress.com Site using HTTPRequest to service at https://stats.wordpress.com/csv.php?api_key= ecc...
Need complete http site address (e.g. http://myblog.wordpress.com) and Akismet API key (e.g. 89323243s85b).




